<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Company Insight Software Hackathon</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: navy;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top:40px;
        }

        section {
            padding: 3rem 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 960px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .cta-section {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 0;
        }

            .cta-section h2 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
            }

        .cta-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #007bff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out, color 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

            .cta-btn:hover {
                background-color: #0056b3;
                color: #ffffff;
            }

        .feature-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .feature-box {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 1.5rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .feature-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .testimonial-section {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 0;
            display:flex;
            flex-direction:column;
        }

        .testimonial {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

            .testimonial img {
                border-radius: 50%;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }

            .testimonial p {
                font-style: italic;
                color: #555555;
            }

        .login-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .login-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out, color 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

            .login-btn:hover {
                background-color: #218838;
            }

        footer {
            background-color: #343a40;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            width:100%;
        }
        .img {
            align-items: center;
            margin-left:-300px;
            height: 90%;
            object-fit: cover;

            top: 0;
            left: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="img">
        <img src="/Content/newa.png" alt="Company Logo" class="company-logo">
    </div>
    <header>
        <h1>Company Insight Software Hackathon</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Participate in our own hackathon!</h2>
            <p>Showcase your skills, connect with talents, improve your skills, and develop projects.</p>
            <a href="/Users/Login" class="cta-btn">Login Now to Participate</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="feature-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="feature-box">
                <i class="feature-icon fas fa-code"></i>
                <h3 class="feature-title">Showcase Your Skills</h3>
                <p>Display your coding prowess in our hackathon and stand out.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box">
                <i class="feature-icon fas fa-users"></i>
                <h3 class="feature-title">Connecting Talents</h3>
                <p>Connect with like-minded individuals and form powerful teams.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box">
                <i class="feature-icon fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
                <h3 class="feature-title">Improve Your Skills</h3>
                <p>Learn and enhance your skills through challenging tasks and collaboration.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box">
                <i class="feature-icon fas fa-laptop-code"></i>
                <h3 class="feature-title">Develop Projects</h3>
                <p>Bring your ideas to life by working on exciting projects during the hackathon.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonial-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="testimonial">
                <img src="~/Content/xyz.png" alt="Testimonial Avatar">
                <p>"The hackathon provided a fantastic platform to collaborate, innovate, and learn from the best. I highly recommend participating!"</p>
                <p>- John Doe, Software Developer</p>
            </div>
           
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="login-section">
        <a href="/Users/Login" class="login-btn">Login Now</a>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Company Insight Software. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>

</html>
